original: Lindell, Gilbert Oscar Wilhelm, tandläkare, Amål, f. 2/7/05 i Minneapolis, USA, av fabr. Johan L. o. Hanna Råhlin. G. 33 m. Brita Falk. Barn: Per-Oiof f. 35, Birgitta 38, Gunilla 39, Eva 43, Karin 45. — Studrex. v. Vänersborgs h. allm. lärov. 25, tandl :-kand. 30, tandl. 33. Frakt, i Amål sed. 33, skoltandl. 36-45. Hobbies: segling . o. fotografering.
translated: Lindell, Gilbert Oscar Wilhelm, dentist, Amål, born on July 2nd, 1905 in Minneapolis, USA, son of factory worker Johan L. and Hanna Råhlin. Married for 33 years to Brita Falk. Children: Per-Oiof, born in 1935, Birgitta in 1938, Gunilla in 1939, Eva in 1943, and Karin in 1945. Studied at Vänersborgs higher secondary school until 1925, dental program until 1930, and became a dentist in 1933. Moved to Amål in 1933, worked as a school dentist from 1936 to 1945. Hobbies include sailing and photography.
